{"tid":1516581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘撚入 - 求接力報警驅散廢老","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:27:16.000Z","uid":196227,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6758fd056d597bc8ac37627aa64b620f3fd949","tid":1516581,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"前傳係呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公屋保安開始同警察一樣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511697</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大致係發現藍絲廢老，開始狙擊<br />\n之後再發現黑警般保安，等有時間就去投訴<br />\n<br />\n今日內容：<br />\n我自己狙擊咗4晚，但係都發覺冇人幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟我做既事啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我今日就唔打過去要求代報警啦<br />\n睇下有冇人同路人再決定長期狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wZPRN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wZPRN2.jpg&h=9e8995d9&s={SIZE}\" />住附近唔驚留報案人資料可以直接報警<br />\n<br />\n驚就打去呢個電話2349 4189管理處電話<br />\n管理處有責任去解決，<br />\n<br />\n內容 ： 華塘樓附近有人非法聚集賭博，希望保安或警察去驅散他們。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"4955f8d825abc26ce2900b0bb78936adfcb8ba63","tid":1516581,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"831遊行<br />\n831<span style=\"color: red;\">死線</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a55211c00a06b5a4a834096f93afab6f5a10c5c","tid":1516581,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"求同路人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係住嗰條邨都落力狙擊<br />\n<br />\n附近居民冇理由唔理"},{"pid":"df182a2f7fa4d21021c158efca4ba7112d320ad4","tid":1516581,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4955f8d825abc26ce2900b0bb78936adfcb8ba63","tid":1516581,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"831遊行<br />\n831<span style=\"color: red;\">死線</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"831<br />\n901<br />\n902<br />\n903<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08876fc338c28a5ecca4cef970b311f1c850703","tid":1516581,"uid":231818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"a8eace97966be9541fc74dfcdb1911d99ede866f","tid":1516581,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"開錯台，想轉番去房屋台<br />\n<br />\n算啦，都係冇人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f66f7531a65b40957c44ef6532d16207294693","tid":1516581,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際路線】全世界印依款標語</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifcqnMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifcqnMz.png&h=19bda72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taez0yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftaez0yf.png&h=868ecca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https:/